{"tid":568860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用錢落人地到就好豪，用落自己到就唔捨得","createTime":"2018-02-22T07:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:01:44.000Z","uid":71487,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c4f707f2cfac74b257c78a9d1db2ecf2029b88","tid":568860,"uid":71487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"唔知點解用錢落人地到我就會好豪爽<br />\n例如：成日買電子產品同護膚品比女朋友同屋企人<br />\n或者成日請朋友食飯<br />\n<br />\n但用落自己到就完全唔捨得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似去旅行買好多手信都係送比人 自己一樣野都冇買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己皮膚差想買下護膚品時，一見到價錢牌就即刻停手，但平時又會成日買比屋企人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都想洗下錢落自己到啊，但唔知點解心入面就有把聲叫我唔好買<br />\n買比人地個時佢又唔會出聲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家會唔會咁，究竟其實點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e294cb2c9b74b06f542b8d17f626494da5fa960d","tid":568860,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"屋企人"},{"pid":"fb21b83e849d8974fd1427ccb08876754720dca7","tid":568860,"uid":81505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e294cb2c9b74b06f542b8d17f626494da5fa960d","tid":568860,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"屋企人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"每個人既老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n親戚食飯就搶埋單<br />\n家用又比得少<br />\n以前家姐補習<br />\n要老母變賣珠寶手飾去比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44866a5d0ce314d459271c63cb959e1c8020a04a","tid":568860,"uid":160356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"想人開心多過自己開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ebd7c2d5f96800a9e4975e93dc3219fb8becce","tid":568860,"uid":2323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"自己食餐飯40都覺得貴 但可以買幾千蚊嘅野送比人都可以覺得平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef3b51a91d49e9ee57a45d4d78b0ca45fcbec56","tid":568860,"uid":71487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人學術解答下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人可以慳到份糧一個人洗一千樓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買野比人就幾千幾千咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想洗下錢比自己爽下 個心就會瘋狂叫我咪撚哂錢 屌都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23e013ec8ff7d73aca7c2cbe07ad239989cf3c4","tid":568860,"uid":113830,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"我都係 不過而家諗通左<br />\n女仔廿歲頭慳到護膚品都唔買，以後一定會後悔<br />\n同埋自己都唔錫自己，仲有邊個錫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2839396aa53024db3b91b15215f41c14e5ad63","tid":568860,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"因為某程度上你係投資緊"},{"pid":"880d86729a2aec6ee46e0279d0b31f528b9892f0","tid":568860,"uid":71487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7d58f5a68ebd902a9c7ad624b4c7036f2d5174","tid":568860,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"YES<br />\n<br />\n買比屋企人...佢地一開到聲就話我買啦<br />\n<br />\n同屋企人去旅行住宿食野都好肯比<br />\n<br />\n但買野買GAME比自己就諗左幾日都未買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7387af658912b56a022932bb54ccaab9203d59b1","tid":568860,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"女朋友。。佢成間房所有見到既野都差唔多係我買俾佢，仲有佢部車。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己就著埋D 垃圾T 同著左幾年既鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130d8bf6cb1f424a847c75539bad04c175af37c6","tid":568860,"uid":71487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e294cb2c9b74b06f542b8d17f626494da5fa960d","tid":568860,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"屋企人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"可能真係因爲屋企人潛移默化<br />\n<br />\n細細個成日買新衫褲 但爸媽d衫黎黎去去都得個兩件<br />\n<br />\n家陣大個 唔敢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要好好珍惜屋企人"},{"pid":"0c8e35237b7fc954e327ad8d0a8b4425ad4f2295","tid":568860,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"買野俾屋企人幾萬幾萬咁買<br />\n自己睇中條牛仔褲三千蚊，諗左兩年都未買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7246d6eaaf182ddad6102011b9d23027754d40","tid":568860,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bb8f7b72d855f876526822e65e256ab9308269","tid":568860,"uid":14299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f723d62daa8602ec913e76e1284eed3301995e","tid":568860,"uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"樓主我哋可以做朋友？"}]}